H0.text: Who sang with Serge Gainsbourg on the hit Je t'aime. Brigitte Bardot

H1.text: Who sang with Serge Gainsbourg on the hit Je t'aime. Francoise Hardy

H2.text: Who sang with Serge Gainsbourg on the hit Je t'aime. Juliette Greco

H3.text: Who sang with Serge Gainsbourg on the hit Je t'aime. JaneBirkin

A4.text: In 1969, Gainsbourg and Birkin released the duet 'Je t'aime... moi non plus' ('I love you ... me neither').

A5.text: Gainsbourg had originally written the song for Brigitte Bardot and Birkin said it was 'jealousy' that drove her to sing it.
